&quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\">실무에 적합한 다양한 예제</span><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\">들을 통해 </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\">좋은 코딩을 하기 위한 팁과 학습요령을 알려드립니다.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\">(단, 이 강의는 자바스크립트 입문 강의는 아닙니다.)</span><br></p>', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/JQ_lksQFgNw?si=bm0al9oVyRO-uPLY', 1, 6, '58', '새로운 자료구조 | WeakSet, Map과 WeakMap\r\nGenerator | 비동기 처리, Iterable과 Iterator', NULL);
