 -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\">타입스크립트가 제공하는 강력한 기능들을 제대로 이용하기 어렵습니다.</span><br></p>', '프론트엔드의 피할 수 없는 대세 타입스크립트', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\">이 강의는 단순한 타입스크립트의 문법만 나열해 놓은 강의가 아닙니다.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica 