 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\">해보세요. </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\">직접 오라클을 설치하고 학습 환경을 구축하여 직접 실습해봅시다. </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\">직접 테이블을 구성하고 SELECT, INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE 등의 쿼리를 작성해볼 수 있습니다. </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\">오라클을 활용한 개발, SQL 사용에 대한 자신감을 갖게 될 거예요!</span><br></p>', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/TAyLeIj1hMc?si=kSVbQzMgaUr8QEdC', 0, 0, '198', '이터러블 프로그래밍 | 리스트 프로세싱, if를 filter로\r\n명령형 습관 지우기 | reduce 하나 보다 map + filter + reduce, queryToObject', NULL)