-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\">Java + Spring Boot로 미리 만들어진 도서 관리 애플리케이션을&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-weight: 700; font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\">Kotlin + Spring Boot로 완전히 리팩토링</span><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\">합니다. </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\">모든 리팩토링이 끝나면 다음&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-weight: 700; font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\">세 가지 비즈니스 요구사항과 한 가지 기술적 요구사항</span><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\">을 코틀린 서버 위에 추가로 구현해 봅니다.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\">이러한 과정을 통해&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-weight: 700; font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\">설계 및 구현 관점에 필요한 다양한 고민</span><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\">을 해볼 수 있고,&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-weight: 700; font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\">여러 방법의 Trade-Off 및 장단점과 추가적인 기술</span><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\">에 대해 배울 수 있습니다. </span></p><p><span style=\"